563
00:28:25,337 --> 00:28:26,294
Let me see.

564
00:28:26,377 --> 00:28:27,774
You didn't get much rest, did you?

565
00:28:27,857 --> 00:28:28,857
I've had too much

566
00:28:29,578 --> 00:28:30,737
going on lately.

567
00:28:32,017 --> 00:28:33,414
(Cheng Ying)
Everything is a mess.

568
00:28:33,497 --> 00:28:35,802
I don't have any mood
to come for follow-up treatment.

569
00:28:37,056 --> 00:28:38,056
Madam,

570
00:28:38,778 --> 00:28:40,495
you are responsible for your own health.

571
00:28:40,578 --> 00:28:41,335
If you don't take it seriously,

572
00:28:41,418 --> 00:28:43,245
no one else will
take it seriously for you.

573
00:28:46,617 --> 00:28:48,054
You still have
excessive menstrual bleeding.

574
00:28:48,137 --> 00:28:49,398
Have you taken your medicine?

575
00:28:50,597 --> 00:28:51,877
My health...

576
00:28:54,458 --> 00:28:56,377
No one cares about me now.

577
00:28:57,377 --> 00:28:58,458
What's wrong?

578
00:28:59,017 --> 00:29:00,017
I...

579
00:29:00,377 --> 00:29:02,617
My life is completely out of control now.

580
00:29:03,097 --> 00:29:04,497
My husband is having an affair

581
00:29:05,578 --> 00:29:07,377
and insisting on getting a divorce.

582
00:29:15,377 --> 00:29:17,298
Is anyone there? Please give us a hand.

583
00:29:19,160 --> 00:29:21,465
Madam Zhu, are you here
for her follow-up appointment?

584
00:29:22,377 --> 00:29:24,217
She said her legs feel cold.

585
00:29:24,497 --> 00:29:25,537
I was so overjoyed

586
00:29:25,716 --> 00:29:27,134
that I almost shed tears.

587
00:29:27,217 --> 00:29:29,261
So, I came to ask
Professor Ren to check on her.

588
00:29:29,617 --> 00:29:30,495
We will go in first.

589
00:29:30,578 --> 00:29:31,578
Okay.

590
00:29:32,080 --> 00:29:37,053
(Qibo Medical Centre)

591
00:29:37,377 --> 00:29:39,737
There is a crazy woman who is suing me.

592
00:29:41,857 --> 00:29:43,855
She is giving me trouble at my workplace

593
00:29:43,938 --> 00:29:45,737
and in court.

594
00:29:46,497 --> 00:29:48,698
She is driving me crazy.

595
00:29:49,617 --> 00:29:52,497
My son is still so little.
No one can take care of him.

596
00:29:53,800 --> 00:29:54,800
Cheng Ying!

597
00:29:58,337 --> 00:29:59,337
Who are you?

598
00:30:05,137 --> 00:30:06,578
Meng Meng, are you okay?

599
00:30:07,800 --> 00:30:08,800
No fighting.

600
00:30:12,497 --> 00:30:13,497
Mum!

601
00:30:16,137 --> 00:30:17,137
Mum!

602
00:30:29,650 --> 00:30:30,650
Stop fighting!

603
00:30:30,960 --> 00:30:32,960
They are enemies
who run into each other here.

604
00:30:33,840 --> 00:30:35,079
Xia, calm down.

605
00:30:36,517 --> 00:30:37,517
Doctor...

606
00:31:05,377 --> 00:31:06,377
Quiet, quiet.

607
00:31:08,898 --> 00:31:11,017
It was an accident.

608
00:31:13,658 --> 00:31:15,737
I really didn't mean to do it.

609
00:31:16,137 --> 00:31:20,200
I... I really wish it was me
who got hit.

610
00:31:21,257 --> 00:31:23,103
That's enough.
Do you really want to die?

611
00:31:24,604 --> 00:31:25,604
Quiet, quiet.

612
00:31:30,737 --> 00:31:31,737
Professor Ren,

613
00:31:32,411 --> 00:31:34,930
do you remember when I told you last time

614
00:31:35,857 --> 00:31:38,200
that I suspected my husband
was having an affair?

615
00:31:41,080 --> 00:31:43,080
(Two months ago)

616
00:31:43,200 --> 00:31:44,200
Professor Ren,

617
00:31:44,737 --> 00:31:46,178
is my condition treatable?

618
00:31:46,578 --> 00:31:47,857
30 days in a month,

619
00:31:48,217 --> 00:31:49,826
and I have been bleeding for 28 days.

620
00:31:51,400 --> 00:31:53,183
It's really starting
to take a toll on me.

621
00:31:53,737 --> 00:31:54,977
Is it untreatable?

622
00:31:58,578 --> 00:31:59,977
Actually, your condition

623
00:32:00,080 --> 00:32:01,080
isn't serious.

624
00:32:02,137 --> 00:32:03,877
It's just that the treatment takes time.

625
00:32:04,778 --> 00:32:06,178
This isn't serious?

626
00:32:07,857 --> 00:32:10,054
I started suffering from this
shortly after giving birth to my child.

627
00:32:10,137 --> 00:32:11,497
My son is four years old.

628
00:32:11,977 --> 00:32:13,797
I've been seeking treatment for
my illness for two and a half years.

629
00:32:13,880 --> 00:32:16,014
I have seen many doctors
and taken numerous medications,

630
00:32:16,097 --> 00:32:18,097
but so far, there hasn't been
much improvement.

631
00:32:18,337 --> 00:32:19,575
I have told you before

632
00:32:19,658 --> 00:32:21,014
that in order to cure your illness,

633
00:32:21,097 --> 00:32:23,174
your husband must undergo
the treatment with you.

634
00:32:23,257 --> 00:32:25,171
Tell your husband
to come with you next time.

635
00:32:26,578 --> 00:32:27,977
He won't listen to me.

636
00:32:28,737 --> 00:32:29,737
Professor Ren,

637
00:32:31,497 --> 00:32:33,377
I suspect that he is cheating on me now.

638
00:32:38,920 --> 00:32:40,179
What do you want to do then?

639
00:32:46,977 --> 00:32:47,977
Take some medicine.

640
00:32:49,737 --> 00:32:51,418
I think if you want to get better,

641
00:32:51,617 --> 00:32:53,977
you mustn't be paranoid.

642
00:32:55,458 --> 00:32:57,632
How about this?
Go and collect your medicine first.

643
00:33:08,977 --> 00:33:10,238
Here's your birthday present.

644
00:33:12,783 --> 00:33:14,001
Aren't you going to open it?

645
00:33:16,560 --> 00:33:18,097
My hands are tied. Le Le!

646
00:33:18,977 --> 00:33:19,977
Breakfast is ready!

647
00:33:49,560 --> 00:33:51,080
What do you think? Do you like it?

648
00:33:53,778 --> 00:33:55,538
I didn't know Ferrari made wallets.

649
00:33:55,720 --> 00:33:57,513
These are derived products
of high-end brands.

650
00:33:57,596 --> 00:33:59,076
Hermes even sells lipsticks.

651
00:34:00,257 --> 00:34:01,337
Le Le, hurry up.

652
00:34:01,617 --> 00:34:03,017
Le Le, hurry up.

653
00:34:03,497 --> 00:34:04,497
Hurry.

654
00:34:05,977 --> 00:34:08,178
We're having dinner
at my parents' place tonight.

655
00:34:08,498 --> 00:34:09,577
Get off work early.

656
00:34:09,978 --> 00:34:11,037
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

657
00:34:11,120 --> 00:34:12,494
I have an appointment
with a client tonight.

658
00:34:12,577 --> 00:34:14,294
Start the dinner without me.
I'll come later.

659
00:34:14,377 --> 00:34:15,294
Let's go. Hurry up.

660
00:34:15,377 --> 00:34:16,377
Come on.

661
00:34:24,930 --> 00:34:25,930
Hello, honey.

662
00:34:26,377 --> 00:34:28,058
I received your wine. Thank you.

663
00:34:28,880 --> 00:34:30,415
Why are you being so polite with me?

664
00:34:30,498 --> 00:34:31,498
I'm telling you,

665
00:34:31,617 --> 00:34:33,018
it wasn't easy to buy this wine.

666
00:34:33,738 --> 00:34:34,738
I know.

667
00:34:34,898 --> 00:34:36,857
My husband has been trying to find it.

668
00:34:37,498 --> 00:34:39,218
What's going on? You guys made up?

669
00:34:39,857 --> 00:34:41,214
Not exactly.

670
00:34:41,297 --> 00:34:43,397
That's just life.
There are good days and bad days.

671
00:34:43,480 --> 00:34:44,597
All married couples are like this.

672
00:34:44,680 --> 00:34:46,420
Why did you buy him such expensive wine?

673
00:34:46,857 --> 00:34:48,944
It's your birthday,
but you're giving him a gift.

674
00:34:49,576 --> 00:34:51,016
He gave me a wallet too.

675
00:34:51,137 --> 00:34:52,218
From Ferrari.

676
00:34:53,738 --> 00:34:54,738
(What the hell?)

677
00:34:55,658 --> 00:34:57,534
It's a specially customized edition.

678
00:34:57,617 --> 00:34:59,270
You don't know they have this, do you?

679
00:34:59,698 --> 00:35:00,785
Fine, fine. I don't know.

680
00:35:01,738 --> 00:35:02,857
Remember,

681
00:35:03,178 --> 00:35:05,700
keep showing off your love
might lead to a break-up sooner.

682
00:35:09,938 --> 00:35:10,815
What do you think?

683
00:35:10,898 --> 00:35:11,935
Do you like your car?

684
00:35:12,018 --> 00:35:12,895
Yes.

685
00:35:12,978 --> 00:35:14,014
Thanks, honey.

686
00:35:14,097 --> 00:35:15,097
I'm glad you liked it.

687
00:35:15,418 --> 00:35:17,418
How about taking me for a ride later?

688
00:35:17,617 --> 00:35:18,617
Sure.

689
00:35:48,577 --> 00:35:50,855
I didn't mean to hit her.

690
00:35:50,938 --> 00:35:52,857
I already told her that.

691
00:35:54,178 --> 00:35:55,857
It wasn't my intention.

692
00:35:59,920 --> 00:36:00,920
Professor Ren.

693
00:36:05,418 --> 00:36:06,857
What brings you to my school?

694
00:36:07,280 --> 00:36:08,095
-I...
-What's wrong?

695
00:36:08,178 --> 00:36:09,857
I think I'm losing it.

696
00:36:10,560 --> 00:36:11,560
Professor Ren,

697
00:36:11,978 --> 00:36:13,498
you have to help me.

698
00:36:15,040 --> 00:36:16,040
Where is your husband?

699
00:36:17,018 --> 00:36:18,777
He is cheating on me.

700
00:36:19,522 --> 00:36:21,281
I saw it with my own eyes.

701
00:36:21,364 --> 00:36:23,604
I saw it with my own eyes.

702
00:36:25,604 --> 00:36:27,417
Calm down, okay?

703
00:36:31,640 --> 00:36:32,680
Professor Ren,

704
00:36:32,880 --> 00:36:34,400
I'm losing all my blood.

705
00:36:35,698 --> 00:36:36,898
Am I dying soon?

706
00:36:37,840 --> 00:36:38,961
Don't say that.

707
00:36:39,857 --> 00:36:41,458
It's not that easy to die.

708
00:36:42,498 --> 00:36:44,585
Have you taken the medicine
I prescribed for you?

709
00:36:45,218 --> 00:36:46,218
No.

710
00:36:46,557 --> 00:36:49,694
I... I forgot to take it this week.

711
00:36:49,777 --> 00:36:52,297
You have no idea
how terrible my life has been.

712
00:36:56,297 --> 00:36:58,176
She is a murderer!

713
00:36:58,396 --> 00:37:00,596
She has ruined my daughter's life!

714
00:37:00,837 --> 00:37:02,405
She must be sentenced to death!

715
00:37:03,284 --> 00:37:05,124
I didn't do it on purpose.

716
00:37:05,280 --> 00:37:06,481
And what did you do to me?

717
00:37:06,725 --> 00:37:08,244
You're stalking me

718
00:37:08,405 --> 00:37:09,522
like a lunatic.

719
00:37:09,605 --> 00:37:11,481
She follows me to my workplace,

720
00:37:11,564 --> 00:37:12,642
to my home.

721
00:37:12,725 --> 00:37:15,018
She even posts defamatory messages
about me online.

722
00:37:15,405 --> 00:37:18,405
You're driving me crazy, you know?

723
00:37:18,828 --> 00:37:19,882
-You're going crazy?
-Officers!

724
00:37:19,965 --> 00:37:22,183
-I'm the one who's going crazy!
-What are you doing?

725
00:37:31,005 --> 00:37:34,124
He bought a luxury car for his mistress.

726
00:37:34,764 --> 00:37:36,445
On my birthday,

727
00:37:36,645 --> 00:37:38,562
he gave me the gift
that came with the car

728
00:37:38,645 --> 00:37:40,764
as my birthday present.

729
00:37:41,477 --> 00:37:43,717
You need to control your emotions.

730
00:37:45,844 --> 00:37:47,925
If you lose control of your emotions,

731
00:37:48,188 --> 00:37:50,364
even if I give you acupuncture
or medication,

732
00:37:51,160 --> 00:37:52,322
it can only treat your body,

733
00:37:52,405 --> 00:37:53,685
not your mind.

734
00:37:54,324 --> 00:37:55,445
You hate your husband.

735
00:37:56,280 --> 00:37:58,474
Your hatred will harm your heart,
you know?

736
00:37:59,725 --> 00:38:01,445
The heart governs the blood vessels.

737
00:38:02,160 --> 00:38:05,247
If your blood vessels are damaged,
how can your menstrual cycle improve?

738
00:38:05,845 --> 00:38:07,745
But now every time I close my eyes,

739
00:38:07,828 --> 00:38:09,747
I see my husband and his mistress.

740
00:38:09,965 --> 00:38:11,721
I think about my poor son

741
00:38:11,804 --> 00:38:14,022
who is going to lose his father
at such a young age.

742
00:38:14,165 --> 00:38:15,245
All right now.

743
00:38:15,844 --> 00:38:17,362
You need to calm down.

744
00:38:17,445 --> 00:38:18,844
Stay calm.

745
00:38:19,205 --> 00:38:20,284
Take a nap.

746
00:38:21,748 --> 00:38:22,748
God

747
00:38:23,084 --> 00:38:24,844
must have left you a way out,

748
00:38:25,725 --> 00:38:28,364
but you have to find it yourself.

749
00:38:29,205 --> 00:38:30,205
Do you understand?

750
00:38:31,351 --> 00:38:32,305
I have caused

751
00:38:32,388 --> 00:38:34,868
another trouble now.

752
00:38:35,165 --> 00:38:37,284
Where is my way out?

753
00:38:43,165 --> 00:38:44,165
Go to the front.

754
00:38:44,405 --> 00:38:45,405
I will stay with her.

755
00:38:52,165 --> 00:38:53,685
All right now. Don't cry.

756
00:38:54,324 --> 00:38:56,445
You see, we've performed
acupuncture for you.

757
00:38:59,165 --> 00:39:00,481
Thank you.

758
00:39:00,564 --> 00:39:01,685
It's okay.

759
00:39:01,965 --> 00:39:03,922
-It's okay.
-Thank you.

760
00:39:04,005 --> 00:39:05,005
It's okay.

761
00:39:05,364 --> 00:39:06,364
It's okay.

762
00:39:07,965 --> 00:39:08,965
It's okay now.

763
00:39:10,324 --> 00:39:11,324
Mum.

764
00:39:12,788 --> 00:39:14,397
It's okay, Meng Meng.
Don't be afraid.

765
00:39:15,764 --> 00:39:16,965
That scared me.

766
00:39:18,828 --> 00:39:19,745
Are you okay?

767
00:39:19,828 --> 00:39:20,802
I'm fine.

768
00:39:20,885 --> 00:39:21,885
Professor Ren,

769
00:39:22,165 --> 00:39:23,241
you shouldn't save her.

770
00:39:23,324 --> 00:39:24,844
You should have just let her die.

771
00:39:33,364 --> 00:39:34,364
She's dead.

772
00:39:35,352 --> 00:39:36,352
She just died.

773
00:39:37,604 --> 00:39:39,344
A car will come and take her away later.

774
00:39:42,645 --> 00:39:43,645
It's okay.

775
00:39:44,764 --> 00:39:46,597
Take her to the back and let her rest.

776
00:39:47,324 --> 00:39:48,324
Don't worry. It's okay.

777
00:40:03,084 --> 00:40:04,084
She's dead.

778
00:40:04,657 --> 00:40:05,918
What are you going to do now?

779
00:40:09,828 --> 00:40:11,067
I think

780
00:40:12,885 --> 00:40:14,685
you're going to get sued.

781
00:40:16,245 --> 00:40:17,802
Everyone saw it just now.

782
00:40:17,885 --> 00:40:19,844
You had a fight with her before she died.

783
00:40:20,618 --> 00:40:22,966
You had a fight with her
in the courtroom this morning.

784
00:40:24,124 --> 00:40:26,405
Her husband and her child
won't let you off the hook.

785
00:40:27,038 --> 00:40:28,473
You will have to compensate them.

786
00:40:29,604 --> 00:40:31,005
How much money do you have now?

787
00:40:34,165 --> 00:40:35,764
I'm asking you.

788
00:40:40,165 --> 00:40:41,082
Tian Zhen,

789
00:40:41,165 --> 00:40:42,677
go and give her family a call.

790
00:40:42,760 --> 00:40:44,945
Ask him to bring their child
to see her off one last time.

791
00:40:45,028 --> 00:40:46,028
Okay.

792
00:40:46,645 --> 00:40:47,645
Professor Ren.

793
00:40:49,132 --> 00:40:50,932
Holding onto me won't help you.

794
00:40:55,245 --> 00:40:56,245
Master,

795
00:40:56,628 --> 00:40:58,976
I just saw a dead person
